response.overview: The 2024 NXT Stand & Deliver is a professional wrestling event produced by WWE for its developmental brand NXT. It is the fourth annual NXT Stand & Deliver event and took place on Saturday, April 6, 2024, at the Wells Fargo Center in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. The event aired via WWE's live streaming platforms and was held as part of WrestleMania Weekend, taking place the same day as WrestleMania XL Night 1 with a special start time of 11:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
